---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Chaos With Clarity | Poems + Founder Soul Work">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section style="min-height:100svh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;padding:9rem 3rem 5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;background:#f3e8d8;">

    <!-- Decorative circle — amber-olive blend -->
    <div style="position:absolute;right:-5vw;top:8%;width:clamp(220px,40vw,540px);height:clamp(220px,40vw,540px);border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#c17f3a,#5d6b45);opacity:0.07;pointer-events:none;"></div>
    <!-- Thin vertical line left decoration -->
    <div style="position:absolute;left:3rem;top:0;bottom:0;width:1px;background:linear-gradient(to bottom,transparent,#cec5ad 20%,#cec5ad 80%,transparent);opacity:0.5;"></div>

    <div style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;width:100%;position:relative;">

      <p style="font-size:0.64rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:400;">Poetry · Soul Work · Finance</p>

      <h1 style="margin-bottom:2.75rem;line-height:0.88;">
        <span style="display:block;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(4rem,10vw,9rem);font-weight:600;color:#1a1612;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Chaos</span>
        <span style="display:block;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3.8vw,3.2rem);font-weight:400;font-style:italic;color:#c17f3a;padding-left:clamp(1rem,3vw,3rem);line-height:1.5;">With</span>
        <span style="display:block;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',Georgia,serif;font-size:clamp(4rem,10vw,9rem);font-weight:600;color:#1a1612;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Clarity</span>
      </h1>

      <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:clamp(0.88rem,1.5vw,0.98rem);max-width:30rem;line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:3rem;font-weight:300;border-left:2px solid #cec5ad;padding-left:1.25rem;">
        I am a poet who does founder numbers.<br/>
        A CFO who writes about death and freedom.<br/>
        This is where my soul work lives.
      </p>

      <div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem;align-items:center;">
        <a href="/writings" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#1a1612;text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid #1a1612;padding-bottom:3px;font-weight:400;transition:color 0.2s;">Read Poems</a>
        <a href="https://calendly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.9rem 1.9rem;text-decoration:none;font-weight:400;transition:background 0.2s;">Book Soul + Strategy</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- BELOW HERO GRID -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:4rem 3rem 6rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:3fr 2fr;border:1px solid #cec5ad;" class="home-grid">

      <!-- Latest Poem -->
      <div style="padding:3rem;border-right:1px solid #cec5ad;"
           data-poem-card
           data-title="Unstruck Silence (Anhat Nad)"
           data-date="March 2026"
           data-poem="There is a sound
that was never struck —
no string plucked, no drum hit,
no throat opened to release it.

It was here before you arrived.
It is here after the last thought
you'll ever think
dissolves.

You have heard it in the space
between two breaths —
not the inhale,
not the exhale,
but the pause that holds both,
the way a door frame holds
a house.

You have heard it in the room
after crying stops,
when the chest finally unclenches
and something older than grief
comes through.

The mystics called it Anahata —
unstruck.
The thing that hums
without cause,
loves without reason,
stays without being asked.

You think you have to earn stillness.
You think silence is the reward
for surviving.

But it is not earned.
It is only uncovered —
the way snow uncovers
ground
by melting."
           data-reflection="Anhat Nad is a concept from Indian classical music and tantra — the sound that was never struck. The Anahata chakra, or heart center, is said to resonate with this unstruck sound. I wrote this after a long meditation session where I kept waiting for something to happen. Nothing did. And then I realized — that was it.">
        <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">Latest Poem</p>
        <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.75rem;color:#1a1612;line-height:1.15;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Unstruck Silence<br/><span style="font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:1.25rem;color:#7a7260;">(Anhat Nad)</span></h3>
        <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;color:#7a7260;font-size:1.1rem;line-height:2.2;border-left:2px solid #c17f3a;padding-left:1.5rem;margin-bottom:2.5rem;">
          There is a sound<br/>
          that was never struck —<br/>
          no string plucked, no drum hit,<br/>
          no throat opened to release it.
        </p>
        <button data-open-poem style="background:none;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.22em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c17f3a;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;padding:0;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;transition:opacity 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.opacity='0.6'" onmouseout="this.style.opacity='1'">
          Read full <i class="ph ph-arrow-right"></i>
        </button>
      </div>

      <!-- Right column -->
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;">

        <!-- Soul + Strategy -->
        <div style="padding:2.25rem 2.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid #cec5ad;background:#e8dcc8;flex:1;">
          <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1rem;font-weight:400;">1:1 Offering</p>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;margin-bottom:0.6rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Soul + Strategy</h3>
          <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1rem;">For founders who are financially sharp but emotionally lost. 90 minutes of clarity.</p>
          <p style="color:#c17f3a;font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:300;">₹15,000 · 90 mins</p>
          <a href="https://calendly.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#c17f3a;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #c17f3a;padding:0.6rem 1.1rem;font-weight:400;transition:background 0.2s;">Book a Call</a>
        </div>

        <!-- Newsletter -->
        <div style="padding:2.25rem 2.5rem;flex:1;">
          <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1rem;font-weight:400;">Letters</p>
          <h3 style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:1.3rem;color:#1a1612;margin-bottom:0.6rem;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.01em;">Join the Chaos</h3>
          <p style="color:#7a7260;font-size:0.85rem;line-height:1.85;margin-bottom:1.5rem;">Poems and reflections sent to your inbox. No noise. Just soul work.</p>
          <form action="/join" style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
            <input type="email" placeholder="your@email.com" style="background:#f3e8d8;border:1px solid #cec5ad;color:#1a1612;font-size:0.85rem;padding:0.75rem 0.9rem;width:100%;outline:none;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:300;" />
            <button type="submit" style="background:#c17f3a;color:#f3e8d8;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:0.8rem;border:none;cursor:pointer;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;font-weight:400;">Send Me Poems</button>
          </form>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ABOUT STRIP -->
  <section style="max-width:72rem;margin:0 auto;padding:0 3rem 7rem;">
    <div style="background:#e8dcc8;border:1px solid #cec5ad;padding:3rem 3.5rem;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
      <div style="position:absolute;right:-2rem;top:-2rem;width:10rem;height:10rem;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid #cec5ad;opacity:0.4;"></div>
      <p style="font-size:0.63rem;letter-spacing:0.28em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#5d6b45;margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:400;">Who writes here</p>
      <p style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:clamp(1.3rem,2.8vw,2rem);color:#1a1612;line-height:1.6;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:2rem;font-style:italic;">
        "Spreadsheets couldn't answer the chest ache.<br/>So I write."
      </p>
      <a href="/about" style="display:inline-block;font-size:0.66rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#7a7260;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid #cec5ad;padding:0.65rem 1.25rem;font-weight:400;">About Abby →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .home-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>
